data.description: ASSUMABLE VA! Completely renovated 4 bedroom, 2 bath home in the coveted community of Kenwood.  Extra room with closet could easily serve as a 4th bedroom or office. Beautifully appointed with open concept kitchen and family room. Master bedroom with en suite bath includes large walk in shower and double vanity sink. Full additional bathroom with tiled in tub/shower combo and double vanities. Tastefully appointed kitchen includes stainless appliances, tons of cabinetry, beautiful stone counter tops, and eat in dining area. Additional living room is perfect for a playroom or extra space for larger families. Formal dining off of the kitchen is another reason this house is so versatile and comfortable. Centrally located to shopping, restaurants, schools, golf, as well as Hurlburt and Eglin
